name: Sacrifice N0.09
description:
35mm Film photography Sacrifice N0.09 is the 9th photo of one of my photo series that was captured by me during a trip to a village in the north of Iran. All I can remember from that village is the pain and suffer of those people who lived there to stand up for their beliefs.

Captured by Camera : Olympus stylus mju - Film : Fuji C200 Scanned in the Aria laboratory

File Size : 3024*2004
